Class JStatePublisherActor

  • public class JStatePublisherActor
extends akka.actor.typed.javadsl.AbstractBehavior<org.tmt.encsubsystem.enchcd.JStatePublisherActor.StatePublisherMessage>
    This actor publishes various current states to assembly. This actor have timers for each current state which define schedule/frequency at which current states are published. Each current state has it's own frequency and timer.
